name: Zenland
description: Zenland Fee (ZENF) is an ERC-20 utility token of the Zenland smart contract platform. Token integration with the escrow platform and its deflationary model ensures robust tokenomics and its value-driven utility. Zenland provides blockchain-based smart contract protection to any product or service you are selling or buying online. Because of their blockchain nature, smart contracts cannot be influenced by third parties or a central authority, and are only fulfilled when both parties complete their part of the deal
